{"tid":1641960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警都濫用fact check","createTime":"2019-10-09T13:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T13:46:40.000Z","uid":178777,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce213c38c508ed9afcedfe1bac8dc03a23d6f0f","tid":1641960,"uid":178777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:42:52.000Z","msg":"【 警方澄清 - 港鐵上水站謠言 】<br />\n<br />\n警方留意到有人在社交媒體散播謠言，聲稱昨日(2019-10-08)晚上有警員假扮暴徒，進入港鐵上水站內破壞設施。警方必須澄清，警方因應近日有暴徒在港鐵站進行破壞作出調查，在收到相關消息後，曾調派便裝警務人員進入上水站內執行任務，而所有警務人員絕不會進行任何違法行為。警方會繼續按實際需要，採用不同方式打擊罪案。<br />\n<br />\n#Factcheck<br />\n#止暴制亂 #香港平安 #停止暴力 #向暴力說不<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 講兩句就叫fact check?<br />\n你話係就係 要證明清白就公開cctv<br />\n唔係hashtag fact check就叫到check左<br />\n不過信用破產既人講咩都唔會有人信<br />\n唔好當香港人傻"},{"pid":"ff5f7a7171ebe732e2f50b51e32958544c61e631","tid":1641960,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:44:18.000Z","msg":"宜家要double check"},{"pid":"83137bd662cb64fd3597d0d7c79abe85fd832e31","tid":1641960,"uid":46966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母係查個的士佬啦仆街<br />\n玩你老母fb咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ab7f97249c55eed2446d11a10d08f949d20e7f","tid":1641960,"uid":138462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:45:30.000Z","msg":"真係好肉酸"},{"pid":"714d87d91cd08d24a313981568bab13b9e68d9d1","tid":1641960,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:46:40.000Z","msg":"完全無解釋過，黑警真係on9"}]}